column2: SELECT     m.objid as gal_id, m.ra AS gal_ra, m.dec AS gal_dec,     n.objid as star_id, n.distance,     s.ra AS star_ra, s.dec AS star_dec     into mydb.micadomatches from MyDB.micadostars AS s     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( s.ra, s.dec, #) AS n    JOIN mydb.micadogals AS m ON n.objid=m.objid
